I work near this restaurant and everyday I work I go there and order the lunch special.It is really and you can get a regular meal with pork fried rice.It fits me really well.I usually order the General Tso's Chicken or the Orange Chicken.If I miss the special which is Monday to Friday 11:00 to 3:00 I get their buffalo wings.It is filled with flavor.If you don't like it spicy they will not add any sauce to it.If I work late I can get the Singapore Mei Fun.It is really tasty.They curry flavor filled with the spicyness is delicious.I would recommend this place to anyone if they ask me for a good place to eat.
